        <h2>
            道海玄微的书评 · · · · · ·
            <span class="pl">(<a href="reviews">全部 1 条</a>)</span>
        </h2>
    </header>


        


<div class="review-list">
  
  
      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="3733661">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/3733661/" class="title-link">书很好，校对差</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-3733661"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/1903847/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/user_normal.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/1903847/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">6315436</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-09-25"
      class="main-meta">2010-09-25 18:49:16</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_3733661_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                         虽然错字好像多了些，可是毕竟是经典的作品。这类书有深度的、对道教道家抱好感书毕竟不多。     原来对电子书没好感，认为只有买不到实体书书或是不想买才看电子书，买了该书才觉悟到，买了的书有时也需要电子书的啊。     不过该书还是值得买的。

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">1有用 / 2没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_3733661_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_3733661_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










